collection.name: CREYZIES
collection.description:
CREYZIES are generated entirely from hand drawings by [Reylarsdam](https://twitter.com/reylarsdam). They are the official companion collection to [mfers](https://opensea.io/collection/mfers). This project is in the public domain; feel free to use CREYZIES any way you want.

Official CREYZIES Twitter [HERE](https://twitter.com/CREYZIES)

Official CREYZIES Discord [HERE](https://discord.gg/yTV7B4TT9v)
